description: Unarchives GuardDuty findings specified by the findingIds.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The ID of the detector associated with the findings to unarchive. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: FindingIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the findings to unarchive. (string) ---
